}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "1244-00000813-50Z_ES" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :The device is a [[Edimax EW-7438RPn]].
The FCC ID printed on the label is probably I88WRE2205. :The FCC ID of the parent OEM model is NDD9574381114.
The default SSID may be '''[[ZyXEL]]'''. :Default credentials are from the (draft) FCC manual.
